# Local pattern file for pre-commit hook.
#
# Copy this to `.githooks/patterns.local` (which is gitignored) and add
# any private strings you want to block from accidentally being committed.
#
# Format per line: regex_pattern|human-readable label
# Lines starting with # are comments.
#
# Examples:
#   your.work.email@company\.com|company email leak
#   AB12CD34EF|known company Team ID
#   internal\.example\.com|internal hostname

# your.work.email@company\.com|work email leak
# YOURTEAMID|your Apple Team ID
